    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>chopped onion</strong> to a baking tray with 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min or until the onion is cooked and starting to crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
