    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tomato and onion is cooking, add your<strong> bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with a lid with 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Cook, covered for 5-7 min or until almost all the water has absorbed</p><p>Once done, remove the pot from the heat, fluff with a fork and set aside until later</p>",
