    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated halloumi </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min on each side until almost browning, add the<strong> remaining herb marinade</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min</p><p>Once done, transfer to a chopping board and set aside – this is your <strong>lemony halloumi</strong></p>",
