    {
      "instruction": "<p>Roughly chop your<strong> cucumber</strong> and add to a bowl with your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tzatziki</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> roasted vegetables</strong> and <strong>chopped parsley</strong> to the pot with the cooked bulgur<strong> </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>Mediterranean-style</strong> <strong>veg bulgur</strong></p>",
